{"tid":113313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梵蒂岡反對器官販賣峰會　中國前衛生部長激辯 BBC：陳馮富珍不批評中國","createTime":"2017-02-09T00:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T05:04:42.000Z","uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87122e964f1abfbf389a8c134b53de3cdd9d5cb7","tid":113313,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:45:37.000Z","msg":"中國前衛生部長黃潔夫目前赴梵蒂岡參加「反對器官販賣全球峰會」，BBC形容他在會上與其他與會者激烈交鋒。中國在2015年宣佈已經停止了死囚器官移植項目。但與會者對中國的器官移植項目評批不斷。<br />\n<br />\nBBC報道，黃潔夫向全球醫學界承認，中國器官移植項目改革進展緩慢、非常艱難。黃潔夫2006年首次公開承認中國使用死囚器官進行移植手術，此後於2015年宣佈停止該項目。由於缺乏透明度，器官捐贈者的嚴重短缺和中國長期存在的黑市交易，外界一直對此持懷疑態度。<br />\n<br />\n中國人體器官分配與共享計算機系統負責人王海波在會上強調，中國絶不可能完全控制器官移植活動。因為中國目前有約100萬個醫療中心和300萬名執業醫生。<br />\n<br />\n在梵蒂岡的會議上，中國建議世界衛生組織（WHO）成立一個全球特別工作組，來協助打擊非法器官的販賣。<br />\n<br />\n以色列的移植協會主席Jacob Lavee堅持認為WHO應允許在中國進行突擊檢查和訪問捐贈者的親屬。他說：「只要不對已發生的事情擔負責任，就沒法保證道德上的改革。」<br />\n<br />\n加州大學洛杉磯分校醫學中心的Gabriel Danilovitch博士在會上挑戰中國代表團，稱如果中國不再使用囚犯器官就該直接聲明。<br />\n<br />\n王海波應答稱，他與黃潔夫在過去的12年裏一直在與海內外的批評聲做鬥爭。並稱中國不該被世衛組織做現場檢查。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社稱黃潔夫提供了很少的數據來反駁批評者。他只用了兩張幻燈片來表明近年來活體和死亡捐助者的數量在增加，以及中國近期在努力打擊黑市的器官移植活動。<br />\n<br />\n批評人士此前寫信給峰會組織者和教宗方濟各警告說，中國出席大會是對其過去做法的粉飾和洗白。<br />\n<br />\nBBC報道，梵蒂岡教宗科學院院長索龍多主教為其邀請做辯護稱： 「他們在中國做非法的器官移植？我們並不能確定。但是我們想要推進變革。」<br />\n<br />\n世衛不批評中國<br />\n<br />\n由於聯合國機構完全依賴各國提供衛生信息和統計數據，很少收集或獨立核查政府提供的數據，因此不清楚世衛組織解決器官販賣問題的效力如何。<br />\n<br />\nBBC指出，中國長期以來因其缺乏公共衛生領域的透明度而受到批評。例如，十多年前，在全球爆發嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症（SARS）的過程中，中國最初瞞報該流行病，到中國開始承認疫情的真實規模時，SARS已經蔓延到了亞洲和北美。<br />\n<br />\nBBC提到，最近，中國被批評未能及時迅速分享其擴大的禽流感疫情細節。但WHO總幹事陳馮富珍基本上不批評中國，並讚賞了其器官移植的改革進程。<br />\n<br />\n包括中國在內，世衛組織通常不願批評成員國。例如，在2014年埃博拉疫情期間，WHO延遲了幾個月宣佈該疾病成為一個全球性的緊急情況，因WHO擔心它會冒犯受影響的國家。<br />\n<br />\nWHO去年也未公開抨擊巴西，當時該國最初拒絶共享寨卡爆發的病毒樣本。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%A2%B5%E8%92%82%E5%B2%A1%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E8%B2%A9%E8%B3%A3%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%89%8D%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E8%88%87%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E8%80%85%E6%BF%80%E8%BE%AF-bbc-%E9%99%B3%E9%A6%AE%E5%AF%8C%E7%8F%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25A2%25B5%25E8%2592%2582%25E5%25B2%25A1%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25B2%25A9%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%258F%2583%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%25BF%2580%25E8%25BE%25AF-bbc-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E5%25AF%258C%25E7%258F%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=fd063c97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25A2%25B5%25E8%2592%2582%25E5%25B2%25A1%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25B2%25A9%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%258F%2583%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%25BF%2580%25E8%25BE%25AF-bbc-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E5%25AF%258C%25E7%258F%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F&h=33f7455f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%A2%B5%E8%92%82%E5%B2%A1%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E8%B2%A9%E8%B3%A3%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%89%8D%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E8%88%87%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E8%80%85%E6%BF%80%E8%BE%AF-bbc-%E9%99%B3%E9%A6%AE%E5%AF%8C%E7%8F%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"33c2dece56685b71cd90e00f15f63e7ee50f0636","tid":113313,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:58:13.000Z","msg":"批評之後無人交會費點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcf3711f10705a38ff472ac1f03e6e50465f297","tid":113313,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T01:17:18.000Z","msg":"陳馮富閪條臭貨都唔知憑乜做到主席<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b70b4fc1243fb7dd5a1e9d42c2a93777ffea705","tid":113313,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳馮富閪條臭貨都唔知憑乜做到主席<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港英年代一個2,3線庸才"},{"pid":"5dc38cd1b4e0a511123a59440a7b5b9f76d2120d","tid":113313,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T02:28:05.000Z","msg":"中國人停咗收死刑犯器官，個供給不足去邊度補返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7652c7d373d8d9d8be31956025c0f40304b0b059","tid":113313,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T02:35:20.000Z","msg":"中國會停止器官販賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c2c76427aabc6190530de1735a1431a75c2339","tid":113313,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T02:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國人停咗收死刑犯器官，個供給不足去邊度補返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港近兩年不斷報導邊個邊個等候器官，想立法，香港人副器官夠健康呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bd34fe9ea8e2d6c567e42a1b6e7156a71a41a9","tid":113313,"uid":77697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T02:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳馮富閪條臭貨都唔知憑乜做到主席<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢件臭閪當年喺香港比人屌到反艇，銷聲匿跡左一排唔知點解做左who<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c004c0a039a36360bf0a62c6e58ae81d3f5ce5","tid":113313,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T02:56:00.000Z","msg":"支共捧佢做呢個位，就係要佢做支那走狗。其實呢啲港奸同當年助紂為虐既納粹官員一樣，支爆後一定要清算"},{"pid":"962dca760f94c58337245ae9cba6a13198e7efb7","tid":113313,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T03:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國人停咗收死刑犯器官，個供給不足去邊度補返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法輪大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5b01820241568856925a8a97a28ff5b79c08ba","tid":113313,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:04:42.000Z","msg":"即係之前有用死器啦"}]}